body:
which tensorflow version have you installed? `tensorflow` or `tensorflow-gpu`

- `macos 10.13.3`
- `python 2.7.14` with `pip install tensorflow`, pass
- `python 3.6.4` got same error issues, uninstall first and then `pip3 install tensorflow` fix the problem.
